high_descs: Turn around and head towards the box.
Take the open box from the top.
Take the carton box and head towards the coffeetable.
Keep the box on the coffeetable.
Turn right head towards the sink.
Take the controller from the wash basin
Take the game box and walk towards the hall.
Put the controller inside the box and seal it.

high_descs: Turn around, walk down the hallway and head towards the toilet, then go to the box on the floor to your left.
Pick up the carton box on the floor.
Turn around and hang a right, then walk down the hallway towards the sofa and go to the round table before the couch.
Put the box on the coffeetable.
Turn right and go to the hallway to your left, then go to the sink at end of the hallway.
Pick up the game controller from the wash basin.
Go back to the door way and walk down the hallway towards the sofa then hang a left and go to the box to your right.
Put the game controller into the box on the round table.
anns.task_desc: Put a Controller into a Box on a CoffeeTable

high_descs: Turn around and walk down the hall towards the box, Turn left before reaching the box.
Pick up the box from the floor.
Turn around and walk back down the hall. Take the box to the coffeetable in the living room.
Put the box on the brown coffeetable in front of the box.
Turn around and walk to the microwave, then turn to the left, turn to the right and walk down the hall. Walk into the sink.
Take the game controller out of the sink.
Walk out of the bathroom and go to the living room. Go to the table with the box on it.
Put the game controller in the box and close the lid of the box.
anns.task_desc: Move the controller to the living room and put the game controller in the box.
